cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with computer vision techniques for separating video frames into background and foreground components. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which makes cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper proposes a new technique for obtaining a colored background model, which involves some level of artificial intelligence, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) a possible sub-category. Finally, the paper involves some level of graphics processing, which makes cs.GR (Graphics) a possible sub-category.
